'''現代錦標賽'''（Hyundai Tournament of Champions）是PGA巡迴賽每年第一個賽事<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.pgatour.com/news/2012/06/26/fedexcuppoints.html |title=Fall Series events to offer full FedExCup points |publisher=PGA Tour |date=June 26, 2012 |accessdate=March 13, 2013 |archive-date=2019-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412190310/https://www.pgatour.com/news/2012/06/26/fedexcuppoints.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，開始於1953年，只有上一年獲得賽事冠軍的球員才能參加這項比賽<ref name=sbs>{{cite web |url=http://www.pgatour.com/news/2009/05/07/sbs.html |title=SBS to sponsor season-opening event through 2019 |publisher=PGA Tour |date=May 7, 2009 |accessdate=March 13, 2013 |archive-date=2018-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180612163340/https://www.pgatour.com/news/2009/05/07/sbs.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2013年之前，該賽事是PGA巡迴賽每個賽季的第一項賽事。
